    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The Test conditions factor achieves level 2 against a required level of 3; however, the assessment team determined that the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol is the industry standard for this device class and that inter-laboratory reproducibility provides sufficient confidence. Overall credibility evidence is judged adequate to support a Medium assurance level declaration for this Class II device at model risk level 3. Decision: Accepted.",
